        "subject": "LU-1627 build: use HTTP for ZFS/SPL cloning",
        "message": "LU-1627 build: use HTTP for ZFS/SPL cloning\n\nUse the https://github.com/zfsonlinux URL for doing clones of the\nZFS and SPL repositories, instead of the SSH URL.  This will avoid\nthe need to have an SSH key at github for cloning and make the\ndeployment of new Lustre build nodes easier.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ib95bf61f6f47a0d9c46e8a398d97130cff83cab0\n"
      },
